{"tid":1053460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11歲男割包皮　尿道被誤封！3天無法排尿","createTime":"2019-03-09T05:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T06:06:30.000Z","uid":122,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be58e17a00bb05e0365ac06ecdc656816c0fe150","tid":1053460,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"南非一名11歲男孩去割包皮，結果手術後尿道被縫合起來，導致他3天不能尿尿，到其他家醫院就診後，才把尿道解封。<br />\n<br />\n據《dailysun》報導，2月16日，南非一名男孩給在靠近布里茨(Brits)的非政府組織「JPS Africa」割包皮，但沒想到醫生在他的龜頭縫了幾針，導致他無法尿尿，男孩的母親帶他回診，但是醫生只要他回家拆掉繃帶就好，男孩母親說「醫院只拍了陰莖幾張照片，並給了止痛藥就要我們回來了」。<br />\n<br />\n於是他們到另一間醫院進行檢查，醫生看到後大驚「是誰這樣做的？」之後立即用導尿管幫忙排尿，母親說「裝了2個2公升的瓶子」。2月23日醫療團隊再去探望男孩，表示「男孩傷口癒合的很好」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRCfQ8hsHeq-PEHaJerT7VX5cPqBItE3NIJQlwLYhSUVGurLGed\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRCfQ8hsHeq-PEHaJerT7VX5cPqBItE3NIJQlwLYhSUVGurLGed&h=a25b0272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10cafdcdb14f28b65783e5a739a1eb54946a898d","tid":1053460,"uid":135689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"有冇咁撚誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />4lite"},{"pid":"4417b6d4c4d91b3981b9f28b72d4f7399af9bfd4","tid":1053460,"uid":10157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:51:03.000Z","msg":"一條未來黑腸就咁廢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4d3d66332ff21701cee137ed16904b4423ac68","tid":1053460,"uid":202385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:52:32.000Z","msg":"我搭車忍1個鐘都暈低<br />\n佢點忍到三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會中尿毒咩"},{"pid":"09f0b0bc82b386f9e506ff5ff5dcaea6d906f16e","tid":1053460,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:52:57.000Z","msg":"咁多日冇屙尿都無中尿毒"},{"pid":"905034615bc87ec917cab5d1c8a9db020628818a","tid":1053460,"uid":226048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"聽都覺得急尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4669a9ce0849a4bc381e491386661da692f751d1","tid":1053460,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:05:48.000Z","msg":"2個2公升，<br />\n500mL都夠慘"},{"pid":"993b05ad3c171496717b8284c45e242c31a4de40","tid":1053460,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:06:30.000Z","msg":"圖？"}]}